{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_10_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あの……もう一度確認させて下さい\n莉央さん、マニキュアをうまく塗れないんですよね？",
      "startTime": 4.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうよ。何度も言わせないでちょうだい",
      "startTime": 8.3531974793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません……\nそれじゃあ、今まではどうしてたんですか？",
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "いつもはメイクさんにお願いしてるわ",
      "startTime": 17.4650571507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、頼めない時もあったんじゃないですか？\nブレイク前は、メイクさん不在の現場もありましたよね",
      "startTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "その時は……葵に塗ってもらってたの\nあの子には口止めしていたわ",
      "startTime": 31.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "「やれやれ、莉央お嬢様は世話がやけるな\nまるで執事かメイドになった気分だ」",
      "startTime": 38.1666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "「莉央の面倒を一生見ることになりそうだよ」\n……とか、散々嫌みを言われてきたわ",
      "startTime": 44.6000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵らしいな……\nでも、秘密はしっかり守ってくれたんですね",
      "startTime": 50.6666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。こころや愛にもこれだけは秘密にしてきたの\nだって、年上ぶってるくせに、格好悪過ぎるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 59.4333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、今更なんですけど\nそんな秘密、俺に教えて良かったんですか？",
      "startTime": 66.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "貴方は秘密を守る人だって、信じてるから\n……それに、言ったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 75.4000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "苦手だから、出来ないから断るなんて\n私のプライドが許さないわ",
      "startTime": 81.6333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "了解です、俺も腹をくくります。改めておさらいですが\n今回は、自分でマニキュアを塗ってる画が必須です",
      "startTime": 89.3290555477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "撮影の時は、私が自分で塗るしかないってことね\n……爪以外のところにも、思いっきり塗っちゃいそう",
      "startTime": 98.2000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "前に試した時は、指の第一関節から上が\n全部マニキュアまみれになっちゃって……",
      "startTime": 104.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "絶対、画になりませんし、リテイクですね",
      "startTime": 107.713105329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、いい画になるように、うまくならないと\nいけないのよ。……あっ、そうだ",
      "startTime": 114.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "マニキュアを塗らずに、マニキュアのCMを\n成立させる方法を考えてみる、というのはどうかしら",
      "startTime": 121.9333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ダメです。さっきまでのかっこいい莉央さんは\nどこにいったんですか……",
      "startTime": 128.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "……冗談よ。出来るようになるまで特訓する\nそれ以外の方法を、私は知らないわ",
      "startTime": 135.2666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、貴方も協力してちょうだい。いいわね？",
      "startTime": 138.3414502623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 143.6681396169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、どうしてレッスン室で練習するの？\n私か貴方の部屋でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 148.5333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "自室で二人きりになる訳にはいかないってこと\nでしょうけど、貴方は別に変なことなんてしないでしょ",
      "startTime": 154.3195489775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "信じてもらえるのは嬉しいんですが……\nそれだけは勘弁して下さい",
      "startTime": 161.6829287849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、貴方がそう言うのは分かってたわよ\n時間もないし、早速練習を始めるわよ",
      "startTime": 168.6000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "これ、どうぞ。メーカーさんから試供品を提供して\nいただいたので、本番と同じ商品です",
      "startTime": 175.4240361228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。じゃあ、まずは一度やってみるわ\nおかしなところがあったら指摘してちょうだい",
      "startTime": 183.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n一応、俺もメイクの基本は調べてきましたから",
      "startTime": 187.7000022888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "えぇと、まずは爪の油分を取って……",
      "startTime": 191.2657816412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "手順は合ってますね。動画で観た限り、そんなに\n難しそうではなかったし――って、莉央さん！？",
      "startTime": 200.4501010103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "何よ？　急に大声を出して",
      "startTime": 204.3340251765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、爪に対して横向きに塗ってるんですか？",
      "startTime": 207.0985376359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "この方が塗りやすいからだけど",
      "startTime": 210.7068595251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それだと爪以外にもマニキュアがつきやすいそうです\n縦に、爪の根元から先に向かって塗って下さい",
      "startTime": 217.2999921162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かってるわよ！\nちょっと個性を出してみたかっただけよ",
      "startTime": 223.3333305358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこだわりはなくても……あ……\nマニキュアを落とす時は、リムーバーを使って下さいね",
      "startTime": 229.833315277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "それくらいは知ってるわよ！\n貴方は私のお母さんか何かなの！？",
      "startTime": 235.5999870299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、見てみなさい。綺麗に塗れたでしょ？\nこれなら撮影だって乗り切れるわ",
      "startTime": 244.5666486103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "確かに綺麗に塗れていますけど……\n片手で一時間もかかってますよ",
      "startTime": 250.3627529125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "し、しょうがないじゃない！\n慎重にやってるんだから！",
      "startTime": 255.4999819437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "……大変言いにくいんですが\n全然画にはなってませんでしたし、やはり断るしか……",
      "startTime": 260.2601458634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……大人しく聞いていれば\nさっきから言いたいことをペラペラと……！",
      "startTime": 269.233315277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio027.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに言うんなら、貴方も塗ってみせなさいよ！\nかっこ良く、画になるように！",
      "startTime": 276.4046540807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "俺がCMに出る訳じゃないんですから……\n大体、俺がメイクする必要ないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 281.829106768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio028.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの？　今時、男性がメイクするのなんて\n普通なんだから。爪だけじゃなく顔もやりなさい",
      "startTime": 289.5724206872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio029.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、ファンデを使った方がいいと前から\n思っていたのよね。ルージュも試してみましょう",
      "startTime": 296.9333132425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、俺はいいから、莉央さんの練習を――",
      "startTime": 300.8843229454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio030.m4a",
      "text": "動かないでよ、もうちょっと遊ばせなさい",
      "startTime": 303.9330964089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "今、はっきりと遊んでるって言いましたよね？\n俺で遊ばないで下さいよ",
      "startTime": 309.9333112079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-rio031.m4a",
      "text": "あはははは！　貴方、その顔何！？\nあははは！",
      "startTime": 320.9744461742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_02-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんがやったんでしょう……\nほら、もう遊んでないで練習して下さい",
      "startTime": 326.4999778746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
